thread.title: Julian L
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Julian L

author: Julian L
title: Julian L
text: I was wrapped with their service. I bought two cables and unfortunately one was damaged. I contacted them and they gave me a phone call within a day and sent out a new one free of charge after a quick email and a photo of the damaged product. Excellent customer service. I will definitely buy from them in the future. :D
